Index: 
===================================================================
--- 
+++ 
@@ -0,0 +1,27 @@
+{
+  "manifest_version": 3,
+  "name": "Craigslist to JSON",
+  "version": "1.0",
+  "description": "Converts Craigslist ads to JSON format with a button click",
+  "permissions": ["activeTab", "scripting"],
+  "action": {
+    "default_popup": "popup.html",
+    "default_icon": {
+      "16": "images/icon16.png",
+      "48": "images/icon48.png",
+      "128": "images/icon128.png"
+    }
+  },
+  "icons": {
+    "16": "images/icon16.png",
+    "32": "images/icon32.png",
+    "48": "images/icon48.png",
+    "128": "images/icon128.png"
+  },
+  "content_scripts": [
+    {
+      "matches": ["*://*.craigslist.org/*"],
+      "js": ["content.js"]
+    }
+  ]
+}
